name: Digital Ego TEZ#002
description:
"Augment your Digital Ego in Web 3.0 Metaverse"

How can we see metaverse unfold? It's essentially an universe of infinite, interconnected virtual societies where people can connect, play and work using augmented reality glasses, virtual reality headsets, smartphone apps, and other technologies. And Facebook is trying to seize the term for itself, by doing it's recent rebranding. But will it succeed?

— from “the Guide of Unit-153c" by the Prophet X
